</taxonomicName>
, p. 48, pl. 4, fig. 7.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="4A6336F3FFFFFFBEFC959EC56D207FD4" blockId="18.[831,1437,612,751]" pageId="18" pageNumber="32">
1956. 
<taxonomicName id="8DDC4D70FFFFFFBEFC289EC66DB57FF6" authority="REUSS." authorityName="REUSS." box="[898,1208,642,663]" class="Nodosariata" family="Nodosariidae" genus="Frondicularia" kingdom="Chromista" order="Nodosariida" pageId="18" pageNumber="32" phylum="Foraminifera" rank="species" species="goldfussi">
<emphasis id="78A8EAE1FFFFFFBEFC289EC66D667FF6" box="[898,1131,642,663]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="32">Frondicularia goldfussi</emphasis>
REUSS.
</taxonomicName>
- SAID &amp; KENAWY, p. 136, pl. 2, fig. 36.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="4A6336F3FFFFFFBEFC959EF86AFE7F8F" blockId="18.[831,1437,612,751]" pageId="18" pageNumber="32">
1985. 
<taxonomicName id="8DDC4D70FFFFFFBEFC289EF86DB47FB0" authority="REUSS." authorityName="REUSS." box="[898,1209,700,721]" class="Nodosariata" family="Nodosariidae" genus="Frondicularia" kingdom="Chromista" order="Nodosariida" pageId="18" pageNumber="32" phylum="Foraminifera" rank="species" species="goldfussi">
